longBusinessSummary: Greencity Acquisition Corporation does not have significant operations. The company focuses on effecting a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses. Greencity Acquisition Corporation was incorporated in 2018 and is based in Shanghai, China.
